000BAE  1  73 20 61 6E  
000BB2  1  79 20 6B 65  
000BCB  1               ttl_keys1:
000BCB  1  4D 6F 76 65          .BYTE   "Move: W A S D (or H J K L)   G: guard   T: use/shop",0
000BCF  1  3A 20 57 20  
